p: In the District Court of the third Judicial district of Washington Territory holding terms at Port Townsend
In the matter of the application of Robert Moulton for a writ of Habeas Corpus

It appearing ing to the Court by the pleadings and herein made and filed that the said Rosa Moulton and Mellie Moulton are the minor children of said Robert Moulton, and that they are unlawfully detained by the said James Eaus the respondent herein and the said minor children being now in the custody of the Court. It is therefore considered and adjudged by the court that said children be taken from the custody of the said James Eaves and restorted to the custody and control of said Robert Moulton and that the said James Eaves pay the costs in this case taxed at dollars and that texecution issue thereofre
